  "title": "Logistic Assistant",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u><br /><br />1.  Receiving of incoming stocks and deliveries.</p><p>2.  Packing of goods into boxes for export or local delivery</p><p>3.  Recording of product batch code and checking of product before packing</p><p>4.  Preparing documentation for export</p><p>5.  Getting shipment quotes from courier companies</p><p>6.  Maintain up-to-date inventory records.</p><p>7.  Any other ad-hoc logistic duties as assigned by manager.<br /></p><p><u><strong>REQUIREMENTS:</strong></u></p><p>* Able to handle movements of heavy loads and carton boxes</p><p>* Organised and self-motivated</p><p>* Able to thrive under pressure</p><p>* Basic knowledge of Excel<br /></p>",
